<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <title>About - QuizKaro</title>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: #333;
        }

        .about-section {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 80px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-section h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .about-section p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #764ba2;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #5a67d8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>


    <div class="about-section">
        <h1>About QuizKaro</h1>

        <p>
            Welcome to <span class="highlight">QuizKaro</span>, an interactive platform designed to make learning fun and engaging.
        </p>

        <p>
            Our goal is to help users test their knowledge, improve skills, and grow through quizzes across different categories.
        </p>

        <p>
            This platform is built using modern web technologies to provide a fast, responsive, and user-friendly experience.
        </p>

        <p>
            Whether you are preparing for exams or just love quizzes, QuizKaro is the perfect place to learn and challenge yourself.
        </p>

        <!-- <a href="/login" class="btn">Get Started</a> -->
         <% if (user) { %>
    <a href="/main">
        <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
    </a>
<% } else { %>
    <a href="/login">
        <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
    </a>
<% } %>
    </div>


    <%- include('partials/footer2') %>
</body>
</html>